snippet.title: MODSORK Announce Trailer PC
snippet.description:
Nintendo Switch & PC Winter 19/20!
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/588200/MODSORK/ 

Description:
A mind-splitting arcade game about controlling two avatars at the same time, with interactive music and lasers!

-gesture-driven special abilities: cool moves lead to cool effects
-open-ended Arcade, Progress & local 2-Player Co-op modes
-sound-effects are part of the music: choose from a small selection of musical styles and most sfx in the game are replaced with matching sounds
